==English==

===Etymology===
[[Ancient Greek]] (kausimos), "fit for burning" < (kausis), "burning heat".

===Alternative Spellings===
*[[causinomancy]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# [[divination]] by studying the behaviour of objects placed in a fire. Related to [[empyromancy]] and [[pyromancy]].

